  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Manufacturer for Semi-Con Industry</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Plastic Welder</strong></li><li>Working Location: Loyang</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days (Mon-Fri: 8am-5.30pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Fabrication and assembly: Cut, shape, and assemble plastic parts to make finished products or subassemblies.</li><li>Welding: Use methods such as hot gas, extrusion, or ultrasonic to join plastic parts according to drawings and specifications.</li><li>Equipment operation: Operate and maintain plastic welding and fabrication equipment.</li><li>Quality control: Check welds and finished products to ensure they are strong and meet quality standards.</li><li>Technical interpretation: Read and understand blueprints, schematics, and other technical documents.</li><li>Maintenance and safety: Carry out routine equipment maintenance and keep a safe, clean work area by following safety procedures.</li><li>Record-keeping: Document welding work, including materials used, output, and any issues.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Relevant experience in plastic welding</li><li>Able to read and understand technical drawings, models, and blueprints</li><li>Work with the team to complete assigned tasks</li><li>Follow all safety guidelines, including proper handling of machines and tools</li><li>Willing to perform overtime when required</li><li>Good team player</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#79720 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
